What this gives you:

Native iOS shell that loads full NeuroEdge in WKWebView
File picker support for uploads
Mic/camera usage keys configured
One-command project generation (xcodegen)
Use it:

cd mobile/neuroedge-ios-shell
Set URL in Config.swift
generate.sh
Open NeuroEdgeShell.xcodeproj in Xcode and build.




Set your URL here:

strings.xml
neuroedge_start_url
Build APK:

Open Android Studio
Open folder mobile/neuroedge-android-studio
Let Gradle sync
Build APK from Android Studio menu
